        <div class="scard p-6"><div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Owens Corning Preferred & Owens Corning Preferred</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Dual certifications from the two largest roofing manufacturers in North America — meaning the best warranty options and installation standards for your Oldsmar home.</p></div></div></div>
