      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5"><div class="step-num">4</div><div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Final Inspection & Warranty</h3><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">County inspection for code compliance, delivery of your 15-year workmanship warranty and manufacturer warranty documentation, plus follow-up at 30 days and 1 year.</p></div></div>
